       <script>
        jQuery.ui.autocomplete.prototype._resizeMenu = function () {
        var ul = this.menu.element;
        ul.outerWidth(this.element.outerWidth());
    }

    $(function ()
    {
         var URL_PREFIX = $("#SearchNoFilter_hfUrl").val() + "/select?q=";
         var URL_MIDDLE = "title_querysuggestion:";
         var URL_SUFFIX = "&wt=json";
         var URL_EXTRA = "";

   

         $(".searchboxst").autocomplete(
         {
             source: function (request, response)
             {
                 var selectedValue = $(".searchboxstSelect").val();

                 if (selectedValue === "Subscription")
                 {
                     var subvalues = $("#SearchNoFilter_hfSub").val();
                     if (subvalues === "")
                     { }
                     else
                     {
                         URL_EXTRA = subvalues;
                     }
                 }
                 else if (selectedValue === "Complimentary") {
                     URL_EXTRA = "&fq=(complimentary%3a(true))";
                 }
                 else if (selectedValue === "") {
                 }
                 else if (selectedValue === "Report") {
                     URL_EXTRA = "&fq=(contenttype%3a(Telerik.Sitefinity.DynamicTypes.Model.AnalystReports.Report))";
                 }
                 else if (selectedValue === "News / Blogs") {
                     URL_EXTRA = "&fq=((contenttype%3a(Telerik.Sitefinity.Blogs.Model.BlogPost)+OR+contenttype%3a(Telerik.Sitefinity.News.Model.NewsItem)))";
                 }
                 else if (selectedValue === "Webinars / Events") {
                     URL_EXTRA = "&fq=((contenttype%3a(Telerik.Sitefinity.DynamicTypes.Model.SAWebinar.SaWebinar)+OR+contenttype%3a(Telerik.Sitefinity.Events.Model.Event)))";
                 }
                 else if (selectedValue === "Career") {
                     URL_EXTRA = "&fq=(contenttype%3a(Telerik.Sitefinity.DynamicTypes.Model.Careers.Careers))";
                 }
                 else if (selectedValue === "Page") {
                     URL_EXTRA = "&fq=(contenttype%3a(Page))";
                 }
                 //SAW-93713
                 //else if (selectedValue === "Scheduled Report") {
                 //    URL_EXTRA = "&fq=(contenttype%3a(Telerik.Sitefinity.DynamicTypes.Model.SAScheduledResearch.SAScheduledResearch))";
                 //}

                 // DB - For responsive, check if desktop searchbox is hidden
                 // If hidden, use input from mobile search textbox, if not hidden, use input from desktop search textbox

                 var searchString = "\"" + $(".searchboxst").val() + "\"";
                 if ($("#SearchNoFilter_txtSearch.searchboxst").is(':hidden'))
                 {
                     var searchString = "\"" + $("#SolrSearchBox_txtSearch.searchboxst").val() + "\"";

                 }
                 else
                 {                     
                     var searchString = "\"" + $("#SearchNoFilter_txtSearch.searchboxst").val() + "\"";
                 }

                 var URL = URL_PREFIX + URL_MIDDLE
                 + searchString + URL_EXTRA + URL_SUFFIX;
                 $.ajax({
                     url: URL,
                     success: function (data) {
                         var docs = JSON.stringify(data.response.docs);
                         var jsonData = JSON.parse(docs);
                         response($.map(jsonData, function (value, key) {
                             return {
                                 label: value.title
                             }
                         }));
                     },
                     dataType: 'jsonp',
                     jsonp: 'json.wrf'
                 });
             },
             minLength: 1,
             select: function (event, ui) {
                 $('#SearchNoFilter_hfAutocompleteSelected').val(ui.item.value);
                              
             },
             open: function (event, ui) {
                 $('.ui-autocomplete').prepend('<li><img src="https://www.strategyanalytics.com/favicon.ico"> <i>Search suggestions</i>...</li>');
             },
             close: function (event, ui) {
                 if ($("#SearchNoFilter_txtSearch.searchboxst").is(':hidden'))
                 {
                     $("#SolrSearchBox_ibSearch.ibSearchButton").click();
                 }
                 else
                 {
                     $("#SearchNoFilter_ibSearch").click();
                 }    
             }
         })
     });
       </script>
